reviews.review_text:
Amazing sound, fantastic energy The MOTB crew delivered a stunner with this one.  The sound is impeccable.  If you enjoy full, rich, crisp AUDs, this is definitely worth a listen.  It's FOB with very little crowd noise/clapping.

The performance is pretty darn good too.  The boys are "on" with focused playing from both Jerry and Brent.  The second set has a fast pace with tons of energy.
Sweet FOB recording MOTB srtikes again! This is an awesome FOB recording.
Great show and recording This was the show that hooked me forever. Crazy high energy:  LIG > Deal, and the entire second set are as good as it gets.  Great recording, too.

amazing recording of a classic early 80s blowout I highly recommend this recording!  It sounds fantastic, like you are in the big spaceship Hampton.  jerry and brent are just at the top of their game, and you can really hear Phil thumping away in the background.
